snippet.title: Watchmen on the Wall
snippet.description:
So faith comes from hearing [what is told], and what is heard comes by the [preaching of the] message concerning Christ (Romans 10:17 AMP). This channel is designed to promote Prophetic gifts for the edification and instruction of the Body of Christ around the world.  To God be all the glory!

Feel free to send an email to watchmenonthewall22@gmail.com with any dreams or words from the Lord for use on this channel. You can participate in amplifying the Prophetic gift on the Earth!

Please prayerfully consider supporting the prophets and ministries highlighted on this channel. Links in the description of each video!

To partner in support with the Watchmen on the Wall channel, please consider becoming a monthly member at the link below! Only $10 USD!
